60|$|Saint. Verily, thy beloved is led astray, by {{the young}} man Woodall, that vessel of uncleanness: I beheld them communing together; she feigned herself sick, and retired to her tent in the garden-house; and <b>I</b> <b>watched</b> <b>her</b> out-going, and behold he {{followed}} her.|$|R
